OL,7,FJames Bedding was 15 when he fell from
OL,8,Fthe harbour wall in St Helier, leaving
OL,9,Fhim paralysed.
OL,11,FHe says this news is disappointing, he
OL,12,Fexplains: "It's excluding. It excludes
OL,13,Flots of people with disabilities, not
OL,14,Fallowing them to be involved or have
OL,15,Fthe correct facilities to enjoy these
OL,16,Fevents, it is a huge disappointment
OL,17,Fand you do feel excluded.
