OL,7,FSean Pontin, Chief Officer of Enable
OL,8,FJersey says: "I think it is very sad
OL,9,Fthat we are having this conversation
OL,10,Ftoday, it is 2024."
OL,12,FHe adds: "It is beyond belief and it
OL,13,Fis very sad that we are having this
OL,14,Fconversation.
OL,16,F"Some of the comments that we have
OL,17,Fread on social media are what we would
OL,18,Fsay as an organisation as quite
OL,19,Fdisgraceful to be having these
OL,20,Fconversations.
