OL,7,F"If you look at the ice rink we have
OL,8,Fgot a blue portaloo at the front when
OL,9,Fanybody else can use the facilities
OL,10,Finside, I don't know what that says
OL,11,Fbut I'm sure if we spoke to people
OL,12,Fwith a disability I know what they are
OL,13,Fsaying and I don't think any other
OL,14,Fminority group on the island would be
OL,15,Ftreated that way."
