OL,7,FHowever he says it is something they
OL,8,Fhave not disregarded, he says: "We are
OL,9,Flooking into what other provision
OL,10,Fcould be made to support disabled
OL,11,Fislanders using the ice rink and we
OL,12,Falso have an invitation for non-
OL,13,Fmotorised wheelchairs to be able to
OL,14,Faccess the rink.
