OL,7,F"Last Saturday we had someone in their
OL,8,Fnon-motorised wheelchair come and use
OL,9,Fthe rink and we are looking into
OL,10,Fadditional equipment that we can have
OL,11,Favailable at the rink so if a customer
OL,12,Fcame in a motorised wheelchair, we can
OL,13,Fsupport them."
